# Term Mapping Table

> Maps business concepts, code names, and document paths into a unified domain language,
> enabling AI and developers to use the same terminology.

---

## Usage Rules

1. **Bidirectional mapping:** Business term ↔ Code path ↔ Document identifier
2. **Uniqueness:** Each concept has exactly one canonical term
3. **Consistency:** New documents must follow existing naming conventions

