## New Term Addition Process

When introducing new business concepts:

1. **Determine business term** — Confirm the Chinese name with the team
2. **Determine English term** — Use standard industry terminology (singular form)
3. **Determine code name** — Follow camelCase (variables) / PascalCase (classes)
4. **Determine API path** — Use kebab-case, plural form
5. **Determine DB column** — Use snake_case
6. **Update this file** — Add to the appropriate mapping table

